The Trumphiator Mortar MKIII
Replaces Conference call

The third mortar (fifth if you count the ones that were made but never released)

Ammo regeneration
No self damage (Zero chance of friendly fire)
High projectile count
High recoil
Low accuracy
10 round mag
Very high damage
Great for some carpet style bombing
Comes in all elementals
100% Elemental effect chance
High elemental status damage
Skin exists
Fires in a high arc and rains hell upon EVERYTHING



Complimentary quote from President Donald Trump :D

